    <abstract id="aspace_924251c9dc17ca67c2651349b625f556">Edward J. Malloy (1935-2012) was a labor leader in the Enterprise Association of Steamfitters Local Union 638 United Association and the Building and Construction Trades Council of Greater New York. It contains date books, individual and group photographs of Malloy at events, strikes, and award ceremonies, and other materials.</abstract>
